item.description: Changelog # All notable changes to this project are documented in this page. The format is based on Keep a Changelog. 1.5.0-rc.10 - 2023-10-03 # Added # Significant Performance Improvements with small code changes #523 1.5.0-rc.9 - 2023-09-28 # Fixed # Editor of EditSkinnedMesh components may not work well if the object is inactive #518 1.5.0-rc.8 - 2023-09-25 # Added # Warning Dialog for Legacy Modular Avatar #509 Changed # Internal: ErrorReporting is now on NDMF #511 Declare compatible with VRCSDK 3.
